Portugal’s EU Aid Program Enough for Banks, Premier Says

-- B y   A n a b e l a   R e i s
-- 
2011-10-23T15:22:13Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-23/portugal-s-eu-aid-program-enough-for-banks-premier-says.html
The amount earmarked in  Portugal ’s
external aid program for banks is “largely enough,” Prime
Minister  Pedro Passos Coelho  told reporters in Brussels today.  “Portuguese banks are not in worse conditions than the
rest of  Europe ,” Passos Coelho said. The plan includes 12
billion euros for the recapitalization of banks.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
